   617→
   618→You may pull in just the part of this semver utility that you need if you
   619→are sensitive to packing and tree-shaking concerns.  The main
   620→`require('semver')` export uses getter functions to lazily load the parts
   621→of the API that are used.
   622→
   623→The following modules are available:
   624→
   625→* `require('semver')`
   626→* `require('semver/classes')`
   627→* `require('semver/classes/comparator')`
   628→* `require('semver/classes/range')`
